rows.label: tlk70000045_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Climb stairs straight up to get to
Sachsum Gardens, pride of capital!

rows.label: tlk70000045_01_msg0002
rows.name:
From there, friends can head
to Aquila Watchtower or amble
over to Aureus Palace.

rows.label: tlk70000045_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But not to miss gardens! Beautiful place
of calm, and recently traveling bards
set up with wonderful music too!

rows.label: tlk70000045_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Ah! If gate closed, Rikoko
recommend going round and entering
from side of shopping ward.
